greement with the value\nwhich was estimated, by studying water flows through the Strait of Otranto, to\nbe on the order of 1 year.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 25 Oct 2004 15:31:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2007-05-23"}
